Oh they had - they had a good feed. Yes, I remember once - they had people there that night when I ran away and I left a chicken in the oven. Left it there. I knew I wouldn't get none of that. No. But - them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1534638 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1187644\charrsid860468 Where would you sleep, did you live in?
