, I was there - with Mrs Mere. I don't remember Mr Mere being there when we - had the air raids there. And yet he was somewhere, he was - he died in {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname PlaceName}}Canfield{\*\xmlclose} 
