 Percey - had a boy came home from school, yes, Mr Mere was there then. He was there then. Yet I can't - he wasn't - he was a warden. And yet - he wasn't there - he wasn't there when the - Percy was - he wasn't there when we used to sit in the hall there 
- when the bombings was on. He wasn't there then. And a Miss Dane came. Yet she was to do with the war. Miss Dane used to take the children - evacuees away.
