{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Sloanes Road{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. And then - the black maria. That was a police van. See the policeman pushing the - if they had the - had to knock off - a man with a barrow, you know,
 with - greengrocery or anything else like that, fruit on it, the police had to push the barrow up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1534638 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1187644\charrsid860468 What did they have to go in for anyway?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid5258104 MM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1187644\charrsid860468 
Well perhaps - when you're not - if you haven't got a licence to sell. See? Used to - caution him and all
 that and then - they used to push him up, and they used to have to - you see the police taking the man up, and another policeman push the barrow, he had to do that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1534638 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid1187644\charrsid860468 
